link:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eyt1681415255117.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eyt1681415255117.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eyt1681415255117.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dbm1665702610413\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An area is a development object that represents an area frame on a Form or Report\n    component. It is used to group objects and style the area it encloses. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__section_xbf_ps4_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d164187e50\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Characteristics</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Icon:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__image_oh3_rs4_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/frame_area.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Object type code:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">are</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Main Development Object?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Part of:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rvk1665702582227.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rvk1665702582227.html\" title=\"A Report is a Component that defines the content and layout of printed output of a Uniface application. It is not interactive and cannot be used to update the database.\">Report</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Contains:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" href=\"#\" title=\"An area is a development object that represents an area frame on a Form or Report component. It is used to group objects and style the area it encloses.\">Area</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Generalization:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gya1665702610097.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gya1665702610097.html\" title=\"A Frame is a Development Object that graphically represents a Development Object in the layout of a Form or Report component.\">Frame</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">Specializations:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10628e1_d10629e1_d10630e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/are:<var class=\"keyword varname\">AreaId</var>\n</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__section_dc3_ss4_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d164187e233\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__p_d95789e1_d95790e1_d95791e1\">Area specializes Frame in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__ul_d22_ts4_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38636e1_d38637e1_d38638e1\">It has no code container.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__section_tbt_ts4_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d164187e248\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__p_d95798e1_d95799e1_d95800e1\">Object properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__ul_wdz_ws4_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38639e1_d38640e1_d38641e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38642e1_d38643e1_d38644e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38645e1_d38646e1_d38647e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__p_d95801e1_d95802e1_d95803e1\">Presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__ul_d2z_ws4_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38648e1_d38649e1_d38650e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vsj1665703026566.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vsj1665703026566.html\" title=\"This property specifies a user-defined logical widget that can be used to style the area frame.\">Widget Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38651e1_d38652e1_d38653e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38654e1_d38655e1_d38656e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38657e1_d38658e1_d38659e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38660e1_d38661e1_d38662e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38663e1_d38664e1_d38665e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mok1665702703254.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mok1665702703254.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated horizontally in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Horizontal Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38666e1_d38667e1_d38668e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmf1665702703323.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmf1665702703323.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated vertically in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Vertical Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38669e1_d38670e1_d38671e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__li_d38672e1_d38673e1_d38674e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__p_d95804e1_d95805e1_d95806e1\">The following properties can be used to style the area\n        frame, based on the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Widget Type</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Frame Widget Style Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\"> Physical Property Name </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\"> Property </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Attach</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bou1665702610816.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bou1665702610816.html\" title=\"The Attach to Window Border (Attach) widget property attaches the widget (or area frame) to one or more form window borders or split bars at runtime. This allows the element to be resized or moved when the window is resized or a split bar moved.\">Attach to Window Border (attach)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderType</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cys1665702610904.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cys1665702610904.html\" title=\"The BorderType property is used to display a flat or grooved border around an area frame, grid, or the default entity widget.\">BorderType</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderRadius</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gkz1665702610994.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gkz1665702610994.html\" title=\"The BorderRadius property causes the border of the area frame or entity to have rounded corners. The degree of rounding is determined by the value of the property.\">Border Radius (BorderRadius)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1 dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n                        Color Properties \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mux1665702611074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mux1665702611074.html\" title=\"The BorderColor property displays a border of the specified color around the area frame or entity. It is applicable only if the BorderType property is flat.\">Border Color (BorderColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorFill</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpd1665702587794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpd1665702587794.html\" title=\"Determines whether the background color is styled with a flat or gradient color.\">Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackcolorStart</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kto1665702611220.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kto1665702611220.html\" title=\"The BackColorStart widget property determines the color used at the start of a gradient background in an area frame for entity. The default is white.\">Gradient Color Start (BackColorStart)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">GradientStart</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mat1665702611295.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mat1665702611295.html\" title=\"The GradientStart property defines the edge of the area frame or entity from which to start shading the gradient background color. The shading ends at the opposite side.\">Gradient Start ( GradientStart)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">DropShadowColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecy1665702611370.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecy1665702611370.html\" title=\"The DropShadowColor property causes the area frame or entity to be displayed with a 4-pixel shadow of the specified color to the right and bottom of the object.\">Drop Shadow Color ( DropShadowColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1 dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n                        Background Image Properties \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackImage</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Halign</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Valign</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Hscale</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Vscale</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">PreserveAspect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dbm1665702610413__table_d10631e1_d10632e1_d10633e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ujj1665702610581.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Area Frames and Lines</a><p>Area frames are objects that can be used to group or separate the contents of a Form component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612946\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612946\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Area Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 An area is a development object that represents an area frame on a Form or Report component. It is used to group objects and style the area it encloses. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: are Main Development Object? No Part of: Form , Report , Component Entity Contains: Property , Component Entity , Area Generalization: Frame Specializations: None Compilation Output: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /are: AreaId Specialization Area specializes Frame in the following ways: It has no code container. Properties Object properties: Name Type Location Presentation properties: Widget Type Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Horizontal Repetition Vertical Repetition Border Index Color The following properties can be used to style the area frame, based on the Widget Type : Table 1. Frame Widget Style Properties Physical Property Name Property Attach Attach to Window Border (attach) BorderType BorderType BorderRadius Border Radius (BorderRadius) Color Properties BackColor Background Color (BackColor) ForeColor Foreground Color (ForeColor) BorderColor Border Color (BorderColor) BackColorFill Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill) BackcolorStart Gradient Color Start (BackColorStart) GradientStart Gradient Start ( GradientStart) DropShadowColor Drop Shadow Color ( DropShadowColor) Background Image Properties BackImage Background Image (BackImage) Halign Horizontal Alignment (Halign) Valign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) Hscale Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Vscale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) PreserveAspect Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Related Links Area Frames and Lines Area frames are objects that can be used to group or separate the contents of a Form component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}